rows.label: tlk47300169_01_msg0001
rows.name:
You can get to Superbia from Rigitte
Harbor, and there's a regular service
to Acedia here at Yeshiva Harbor.

rows.label: tlk47300169_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I say "regular," but they can delay
the journey a fair bit if you aren't
carrying a certain amount of cargo.

rows.label: tlk47300169_01_msg0004
rows.name:
We could really do with a proper
service.
